data.description: Stunning 3 bed, 2.5 bath Cave Creek home with a loft! Soaring ceilings, updated luxury vinyl plank flooring, custom shutters, & a cozy fireplace create a welcoming atmosphere. The kitchen boasts white cabinets, corian countertops, & a large walk-in pantry. Primary bathroom has been completely remodeled with modern fixtures & finishes. Seated on a premier corner lot with a little over 12k sqft, this entertainer's backyard comes complete with a covered patio, turf, & a freshly resurfaced pebble tec pool with variable speed pump. This home also offers a 2-car garage with overhead storage, fresh exterior paint, soft water system, new roof, 2 new HVAC units, & solar panels. Enjoy the peaceful community of Tatum Ranch with quick access to St Route 101, shopping, dining, & more!
